(93, 92, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306032649, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Aggressive NPCs and staff accounts', 'Quite simple, but could be useful... What this does is basically checks the victim of an aggressive NPC.\n\nOpen your Npc class, and find your findVictim method, and within that method, add:\n\n[code:h2b1zteb]\n                        if((p&#46;isAdmin()) || (p&#46;isMod()) || (p&#46;isPMod()) || (p&#46;isEvent())) {\n                            continue;\n                        }\n[/code:h2b1zteb]Very simple, but is quite useful....\n\n\n[15:06] Yong Min: That code will make it so aggressive npcs wont attack mods, pmods, admins and event team\n\n[quote=&quot;Yong Min&quot;:h2b1zteb][QUOTE=kRiStOf;311]Developer included in this?[/quote:h2b1zteb]\n\nNot in the code above, however, if you want to include developers from being attacked too, then use:\n\n[code:h2b1zteb]\n            if((victim&#46;isAdmin()) || (victim&#46;isMod()) || (victim&#46;isPMod()) || (victim&#46;isEvent()) || (victim&#46;isDeveloper())) {\n                actionSender&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You can\'t attack a member of staff!&quot;);\n                resetFollowing();\n                return false;\n            }\n[/code:h2b1zteb]You can also define all staff members in one boolean, which will make it easier than having to type all that shit out... Such as:\n\n[code:h2b1zteb]\n            if(victim&#46;isStaff()) {\n                actionSender&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You can\'t attack a member of staff!&quot;);\n                resetFollowing();\n                return false;\n            }\n[/code:h2b1zteb]And define the boolean isStaff -\n\n[code:h2b1zteb]\n    public boolean isStaff() {\n        return isEvent() || isDeveloper() || isPMod() || isMod() || isAdmin();\n    }\n[/code:h2b1zteb]\n\nThe boolean to define isStaff goes in your Player class.\n\nAlso, the prevention of attacking staff members is in the Player class on the \'checkAttack\' method. Add it above:\n\n[code:h2b1zteb]\nint myWildLvl = getLocation()&#46;wildernessLevel();\n[/code:h2b1zteb][/quote]', '261d67650078dc9a2f0c184931652319', 0, 'gIA=', 'h2b1zteb', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(94, 93, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306032703, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Mithril seeds', 'How fun was Mithril Seeds for pissing people off? Remember the good old days?\n\nOpen your InvActionHandler class, and find:\n\n[code:3it4zqpu]\ncase 597&#58; // Charged Dragonstone amulet\n[/code:3it4zqpu]Above that, add:\n\n[code:3it4zqpu]\n                case 796&#58; // Mithril Seed\n                    if((world&#46;getTile(player&#46;getLocation())&#46;hasGameObject()) || (world&#46;getTile(player&#46;getLocation())&#46;hasPlayersExcept(player))) {\n                        player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You can\'t plant a mithril seed here!&quot;);\n                        return;\n                    }\n                    player&#46;getInventory()&#46;remove(796, 1);\n                    player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendInventory();\n                    GameObject tree = new GameObject(player&#46;getLocation(), 490, 0, 0);\n                    world&#46;registerGameObject(tree);\n                    world&#46;delayedRemoveObject(tree, 60000);\n                    break;\n[/code:3it4zqpu]\n\nYou might want to throw in a message to display when the tree has been planted.\n\n[code:3it4zqpu]\nplayer&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You open the mithril seed and plant a tree!&quot;);\n[/code:3it4zqpu]\n\n[QUOTE=Marwolf;472]It looks like [code:3it4zqpu]hasPlayersExcept[/code:3it4zqpu] cannot find symbol in Players.java.[/QUOTE]\n\nDoH!\n\nAdd this into your ActiveTile class:\n\n[code:3it4zqpu]\n    public boolean hasPlayersExcept(Player player) {\n        List playersExcept = players;\n        playersExcept&#46;remove(player);\n        return ((playersExcept != null) &amp;&amp; (playersExcept&#46;size() &gt; 0));\n    }\n[/code:3it4zqpu]And add this to your InvActionHandler class:\n\n[code:3it4zqpu]\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;ActiveTile;\n[/code:3it4zqpu]', 'abb2652f2df3312a6d17abd7b2c70ae0', 0, 'AIA=', '3it4zqpu', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(95, 94, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306032739, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Setting up cannons', 'This will basically allow you to set up your cannons. You can\'t set up a cannon if the tile already has an object on it.\n\nNow the code... Firstly, open your InvActionHandler class and find:\n\n[code:3o8zhmqh]\nelse if(item&#46;getDef()&#46;getCommand()&#46;equalsIgnoreCase(&quot;drink&quot;)) {\n[/code:3o8zhmqh]Above that, add:\n\n[code:3o8zhmqh]\n        else if(item&#46;getDef()&#46;getCommand()&#46;equalsIgnoreCase(&quot;set down&quot;)) {\n            if(world&#46;getTile(player&#46;getLocation())&#46;hasGameObject()) {\n                player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You can\'t set up a cannon here&#46; Please move to another tile!&quot;);\n                return;\n            }\n            player&#46;resetPath();\n            player&#46;setBusy(true);\n            player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You begin setting up your cannon&#46;&#46;&quot;);\n            Bubble cannon = new Bubble(player, 1032);\n            for(Player pl &#58; player&#46;getViewArea()&#46;getPlayersInView()) {\n                pl&#46;informOfBubble(cannon);\n            }\n            world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                public void action() {\n                    owner&#46;getInventory()&#46;remove(1032, 1);\n                    owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendInventory();\n                    GameObject cannons = new GameObject(owner&#46;getLocation(), 946, 0, 0);\n                    world&#46;registerGameObject(cannons);\n                    owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You have set up the cannon base&#46;&#46;&quot;);\n                    owner&#46;setBusy(false);\n                }\n            });\n        }\n[/code:3o8zhmqh]Now open your InvUseOnObject class and find:\n\n[code:3o8zhmqh]\ncase 282&#58; // Fountain of Heroes\n[/code:3o8zhmqh]Above that, add:\n\n[code:3o8zhmqh]\n                        case 946&#58; // Cannon Base\n                            if(!itemId(new int&#91;&#93;{1033})) {\n                                owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Nothing interesting happens&#46;&quot;);\n                                return;\n                            }\n                            owner&#46;setBusy(true);\n                            Bubble base = new Bubble(owner, 1033);\n                            for(Player p &#58; owner&#46;getViewArea()&#46;getPlayersInView()) {\n                                p&#46;informOfBubble(base);\n                            }\n                            owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You add the stand to the cannon base&#46;&#46;&quot;);\n                            world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(owner) {\n                                public void action() {\n                                    owner&#46;getInventory()&#46;remove(1033, 1);\n                                    owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendInventory();\n                                    world&#46;unregisterGameObject(object);\n                                    final GameObject cannonBase = new GameObject(object&#46;getLocation(), 947, 0, 0);\n                                    world&#46;registerGameObject(cannonBase);\n                                    owner&#46;setBusy(false);\n                                }\n                            });\n                            break;\n                        case 947&#58; // Cannon Barrel\n                            if(!itemId(new int&#91;&#93;{1034})) {\n                                owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Nothing interesting happens&#46;&quot;);\n                                return;\n                            }\n                            owner&#46;setBusy(true);\n                            Bubble barrel = new Bubble(owner, 1034);\n                            for(Player p &#58; owner&#46;getViewArea()&#46;getPlayersInView()) {\n                                p&#46;informOfBubble(barrel);\n                            }\n                            owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You add the barrels to the cannon&#46;&#46;&quot;);\n                            world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(owner) {\n                                public void action() {\n                                    owner&#46;getInventory()&#46;remove(1034, 1);\n                                    owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendInventory();\n                                    world&#46;unregisterGameObject(object);\n                                    final GameObject cannonBarrel = new GameObject(object&#46;getLocation(), 948, 0, 0);\n                                    world&#46;registerGameObject(cannonBarrel);\n                                    owner&#46;setBusy(false);\n                                }\n                            });\n                            break;\n                        case 948&#58; // Cannon Furnace\n                            if(!itemId(new int&#91;&#93;{1035})) {\n                                owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Nothing interesting happens&#46;&quot;);\n                                return;\n                            }\n                            owner&#46;setBusy(true);\n                            Bubble furnace = new Bubble(owner, 1035);\n                            for(Player p &#58; owner&#46;getViewArea()&#46;getPlayersInView()) {\n                                p&#46;informOfBubble(furnace);\n                            }\n                            owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You add the furnace to the cannon&#46;&#46;&quot;);\n                            world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(owner) {\n                                public void action() {\n                                    owner&#46;getInventory()&#46;remove(1035, 1);\n                                    owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendInventory();\n                                    world&#46;unregisterGameObject(object);\n                                    final GameObject cannonFurnace = new GameObject(object&#46;getLocation(), 943, 0, 0);\n                                    world&#46;registerGameObject(cannonFurnace);\n                                    owner&#46;setBusy(false);\n                                }\n                            });\n                            break;\n[/code:3o8zhmqh]', 'bd196adad8423d10d101a8c2655d6a98', 0, 'AIA=', '3o8zhmqh', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(96, 95, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306032760, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'BSH NPC scripting methods', 'If you are using xEnts scripting system for NPCs, here is the possible things you can use with it:\n\n[code:1buka2v1]\nSendMessage(&quot;message&quot;);\nSendBoxMessage(&quot;message&quot;);\nAddItem(id, amount);\nPlayerTalk(&quot;message&quot;);\nNpcTalk(&quot;message&quot;);\nWait(length);\nPickOption(&quot;string1&quot;, &quot;string2&quot;);\nTeleport(x, y);\nRemoveAllItem(id);\nHasItem(id, amount);\nRemoveItem(id, amount);\nAddExp(stat, amount);\nGetInventoryFreeSpace();\nGetStatMaxLevel(stat);\nGetStatCurLevel(stat);\nAddBankItem(id, amount);\nCountItem(id);\n[/code:1buka2v1]Note: The pick option method is defined to a maximum of 7.\n\nIf you want help adding more methods to the scripting system, let me know.', 'c3d499bb7302a9482c4453f8a0114563', 0, 'AIA=', '1buka2v1', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(97, 96, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306032777, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'NPC + Object autospawning', 'I developed it out of a need for a faster way of mapping objects and NPCs while in game as I have been constructing large areas for my landscape. You can run wild with the code, have it set the NPC maxX, maxY, minX, minY boundaries, the object type, heck, go for spawning items on the ground too. This is just enough to get most mapping needs taken care of as it has mine.\n\nThe code works in this way:\nObjects:\n1. :spawn OBJECTID DIRECTION\n2. object spawns pointing in the direction specified (0 - 4)\n3. object_autospawn.txt records a XML entry for that object and the direction it is pointing\n4. you open object_autospawn.txt and copy and paste the XML entries into your GameObjectLoc.xml file.\n5. compress GameObjectLoc.xml.gz, erase everything in object_autospawn.txt, restart world server, start again.\n\nNPCs:\n1. ::nspawn NPCID\n2. npc spawns walking randomly within 2 tiles in all directions from your coordinates\n3. npc vanishes after 10+ minutes\n4. npc_autospawn.txt records a XML entry for that NPC with +2 tiles in all directions of the current coordinates\n5. you open npc_autospawn.txt and copy and paste the XML entries into your NpcLoc.xml file.\n6. compress NpcLoc.xml.gz, erase everything in npc_autospawn.txt, restart world server, start again.\n\n\n\nDirections:\nopen:\nsrc\\org\\rscdaemon\\server\\model\\Player.java\n\nAt the top, make sure you have these inserts:\n[code:cqic8phv]import java&#46;io&#46;BufferedWriter;\nimport java&#46;io&#46;FileWriter; [/code:cqic8phv]find:\n[code:cqic8phv]private boolean requiresOfferUpdate = false;[/code:cqic8phv]Below that, paste:\n[code:cqic8phv]public void npcautospawn(int npcid ,int getx, int getX2, int gety, int getY2)\n        {\n                        try {\n                                getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Writing npcid&#58; &quot; +npcid+ &quot; at X&#58; &quot; +getX()+ &quot; Y&#58; &quot; +getY());\n                                BufferedWriter out = new BufferedWriter(new FileWriter(&quot;npc_autospawn&#46;txt&quot;, true));\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;&lt;NPCLoc&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;  &lt;id&gt;&quot; +npcid+ &quot;&lt;/id&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;  &lt;startX&gt;&quot; +getX()+ &quot;&lt;/startX&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;  &lt;startY&gt;&quot; +getY()+ &quot;&lt;/startY&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();                              \n                                out&#46;write(&quot;  &lt;minX&gt;&quot; +getx+ &quot;&lt;/minX&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;  &lt;maxX&gt;&quot; +getX2+ &quot;&lt;/maxX&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;  &lt;minY&gt;&quot; +gety+ &quot;&lt;/minY&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;  &lt;maxY&gt;&quot; +getY2+ &quot;&lt;/maxY&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;&lt;/NPCLoc&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                        out&#46;close();\n\n                        } catch (IOException e)\n                        {\n                                System&#46;out&#46;println(e&#46;getMessage());\n                        }                      \n                      \n        }\n        public void objectautospawn(int objectid ,int getx, int gety, int dir2)\n        {\n                        try {\n                                getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Writing objectid&#58; &quot; +objectid+ &quot; at X&#58; &quot; +getX()+ &quot; Y&#58; &quot; +getY());\n                                BufferedWriter out = new BufferedWriter(new FileWriter(&quot;object_autospawn&#46;txt&quot;, true));\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;&lt;GameObjectLoc&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;  &lt;id&gt;&quot; +objectid+ &quot;&lt;/id&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;  &lt;x&gt;&quot; +getX()+ &quot;&lt;/x&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;  &lt;y&gt;&quot; +getY()+ &quot;&lt;/y&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();                              \n                                out&#46;write(&quot;  &lt;direction&gt;&quot; +dir2+ &quot;&lt;/direction&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;  &lt;type&gt;0&lt;/type&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                                out&#46;write(&quot;&lt;/GameObjectLoc&gt;&quot;);\n                                out&#46;newLine();\n                        out&#46;close();\n\n                        } catch (IOException e)\n                        {\n                                System&#46;out&#46;println(e&#46;getMessage());\n                        }                      \n                      \n        }[/code:cqic8phv]Save player.java and go find:\nsrc\\org\\rscdaemon\\server\\packethandler\\client\\CommandHandler.java\n\ninside, find:\n[code:cqic8phv]if(!player&#46;isAdmin()) {\n                        return;\n                }[/code:cqic8phv]\nBelow, paste this:\n[code:cqic8phv]if(cmd&#46;equals(&quot;nspawn&quot;)) {\n                        int npcid = Integer&#46;parseInt(args&#91;0&#93;);\n                        int getx = player&#46;getX();\n                        int gety = player&#46;getY();\n                        int getY2 = player&#46;getY();\n                        int getX2 = player&#46;getX();\n                      \n                        player&#46;npcautospawn(npcid, getx -2, getX2 + 2, gety - 2, getY2 + 2);\n                                                if(args&#46;length != 1) {\n                                player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Invalid args&#46; Syntax&#58; NPC id&quot;);\n                                return;\n                        }\n                        int id = Integer&#46;parseInt(args&#91;0&#93;);\n                        if(EntityHandler&#46;getNpcDef(id) != null) {\n                                final Npc n = new Npc(id, player&#46;getX(), player&#46;getY(), player&#46;getX() - 2, player&#46;getX() + 2, player&#46;getY() - 2, player&#46;getY() + 2);\n                                n&#46;setRespawn(false);\n                                world&#46;registerNpc(n);\n                                if(player&#46;isMod()){\n                                        world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new SingleEvent(null, 1960000) {\n                                                public void action() {\n                                                        Mob opponent = n&#46;getOpponent();\n                                                        if(opponent != null) {\n                                                                opponent&#46;resetCombat(CombatState&#46;ERROR);\n                                                        }\n                                                        n&#46;resetCombat(CombatState&#46;ERROR);\n                                                        world&#46;unregisterNpc(n);\n                                                        n&#46;remove();\n                                                }\n                                        });\n                                }\n                                Logger&#46;mod(player&#46;getUsername() + &quot; spawned a &quot; + n&#46;getDef()&#46;getName() + &quot; at &quot; + player&#46;getLocation()&#46;toString());\n                        }\n                        else {\n                                player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Invalid id&quot;);\n                        }\n                        return;\n                }\n                if(cmd&#46;equals(&quot;ospawn&quot;)) {\n                                                int objectid = Integer&#46;parseInt(args&#91;0&#93;);\n                        int dir2 = Integer&#46;parseInt(args&#91;1&#93;);\n                                                int getx = player&#46;getX();\n                        int gety = player&#46;getY();\n                      \n                        player&#46;objectautospawn(objectid, getx, gety, dir2);\n                        if(args&#46;length &lt; 1 || args&#46;length &gt; 2) {\n                                player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Invalid args&#46; Syntax&#58; OBJECT id &#91;direction&#93;&quot;);\n                                return;\n                        }\n                        int id = Integer&#46;parseInt(args&#91;0&#93;);\n                        if(id &lt; 0) {\n                                GameObject object = world&#46;getTile(player&#46;getLocation())&#46;getGameObject();\n                                if(object != null) {\n                                        world&#46;unregisterGameObject(object);\n                                }\n                        }\n                        else if(EntityHandler&#46;getGameObjectDef(id) != null) {\n                                int dir = args&#46;length == 2 ? Integer&#46;parseInt(args&#91;1&#93;) &#58; 0;\n                                world&#46;registerGameObject(new GameObject(player&#46;getLocation(), id, dir, 0));\n                        }\n                        else {\n                                player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Invalid id&quot;);\n                        }\n                        return;\n                }[/code:cqic8phv]Save CommandHandler.java and go back to your main server folder. (Where compile.bat is located, noob!)\n\nCreate two .txt files, name one &quot;npc_autospawn.txt&quot; and the other &quot;object_autospawn.txt&quot;\n\n\nCompile and log in game and start mapping. Remember, you must copy and paste the XML entries from the autospawn text files into your Loc conf files and compress them as when you close and re-open the world server, it will forget everything you spawned if you have not written it permanently.', '39284c402f20a98575531f0d6a5adbc7', 0, 'AIA=', 'cqic8phv', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(98, 97, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306032804, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Mining + pickaxe swings', 'Ok here is the actual swings according to Brandon...\n\n[code:h2g50xkk]\n    public static int getPickaxeSwings(int pickaxeId) {\n        /**\n         * Set a default amount of pickaxe swings\n         * for any pickaxe that isn\'t in the switch\n         */\n        int pickaxeSwings = 2;\n        switch(pickaxeId) {\n            case 1258&#58; // Iron Pickaxe\n                pickaxeSwings = 4;\n                break;\n            case 1259&#58; // Steel Pickaxe\n                pickaxeSwings = 6;\n                break;\n            case 1260&#58; // Mithril Pickaxe\n                pickaxeSwings = 8;\n                break;\n            case 1261&#58; // Adamantite Pickaxe\n                pickaxeSwings = 10;\n                break;\n            case 1262&#58; // Rune Pickaxe\n                pickaxeSwings = 12;\n        }\n        return pickaxeSwings;\n    }\n[/code:h2g50xkk]If you are wondering why bronze isn\'t there, you should also notice I changed the default swings to 2, as bronze pick swings twice, apparently...\n\nIt\'s not needed in the cases, as any pickaxe used out of the case with swing by default (2).', 'a775753561bb3a5136b6e5c63115d99f', 0, 'AIA=', 'h2g50xkk', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(99, 98, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306032836, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'BSH integration', '1.) Copy the bsh.jar file from BeyondRSC\'s lib folder and put it in your server\'s lib folder.\n2.) Create a folder in the root of your game server folder named &quot;scripts&quot;\n3.) Copy some of the BeyondRSC .bsh files from it\'s scripts folder and learn how to write your own.\n4.) Create .bsh text files inside the scripts folder (or copy BeyondRSC\'s) for your server and edit your server files to read them as explained below:\n\nAll you need to do is save them as I wrote the names, for example: 098 - Dr Harlow.BSH\n\nOnce saved as a BSH extension, just throw them in your \'scripts\' DIR and run the server. Once you talk to an NPC in game that contains the same ID within the BSH script, it will handle the talking...\n\nFrom the TalkToNpcHandler class:\n\n[code:3cmci2hi]\n                if(world&#46;npcScripts&#46;containsKey(affectedNpc&#46;getID())) {\n                    owner&#46;setBusy(true);\n                    affectedNpc&#46;blockedBy(owner);\n                    if(owner&#46;interpreterThread != null) {\n                        try {\n                            owner&#46;interpreterThread&#46;stop();\n                        } catch(Exception e) {\n\n                        }\n                    }\n\n                    owner&#46;interpreterThread = new Thread(new Runnable() {\n                        public void run() {        \n                            try {\n                                new org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;Script(owner, affectedNpc);    \n                                owner&#46;setBusy(false);\n\n                                affectedNpc&#46;unblock();\n                            }\n                            catch(Exception e) {\n                                if(!(e instanceof InvocationTargetException)) {\n                                    e&#46;printStackTrace();\n                                }\n                                System&#46;out&#46;println(affectedNpc&#46;getID());\n                                affectedNpc&#46;unblock();\n                                owner&#46;setBusy(false);\n                            }\n                        }\n                    });\n                    owner&#46;interpreterThread&#46;start();\n                }\n                else                \n                      if(handler != null) {\n                          try {\n                              handler&#46;handleNpc(affectedNpc, owner);\n                          }\n                          catch(Exception e) {\n                        Logger&#46;error(&quot;Exception with npc&#91;&quot; + affectedNpc&#46;getIndex() + &quot;&#93; from &quot; + owner&#46;getUsername() + &quot; &#91;&quot; + owner&#46;getCurrentIP() + &quot;&#93;&#58; &quot; + e&#46;getMessage());\n                        owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendLogout();\n                        owner&#46;destroy(false);\n                          }\n                      }  else{owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;The &quot; + affectedNpc&#46;getDef()&#46;getName() + &quot; does not appear interested in talking to you&#46;&quot;);}\n            }\n          });\n    }\n[/code:3cmci2hi]', '6d36ad5ec7e550c2e1ccdbdda0e3b2ec', 0, 'AIA=', '3cmci2hi', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(100, 99, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306032863, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'DARScape disk of returning', 'This is how it is for using the disk in DARScape (it teleports to Varrock):\n\n\n[code:1uzerlf2]case 387&#58; // Disk of Returning\n                    if(player&#46;getLocation()&#46;wildernessLevel() &gt;= 30 || (player&#46;getLocation()&#46;inModRoom() &amp;&amp; !player&#46;isMod())) {\n                        player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;The disk doesn\'t seem to work here&#46;&quot;);\n                        return;\n                    }\n                    player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;The disk starts to spin&#46;&#46;&#46;&quot;);\n                    world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new MiniEvent(player) {\n                        public void action() {\n                            owner&#46;resetPath();\n                            owner&#46;teleport(219, 455, true);\n                            owner&#46;getInventory()&#46;remove(item);\n                            owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You find yourself back in Varrock with a sore bottom&#46;&quot;);\n                            owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;The disk has now gone&quot;);\n                            owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendInventory();\n                        }\n                    });\n                    break;[/code:1uzerlf2]\n\n\nWait, sore bottom? What?\n\n[code:1uzerlf2]package org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;npchandler;\n\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;Player;\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;Npc;\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;World;\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;InvItem;\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;ChatMessage;\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;MenuHandler;\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;event&#46;ShortEvent;\n\npublic class Inmate implements NpcHandler {\n    /**\n     * World instance\n     */\n    public static final World world = World&#46;getWorld();\n\n    public void handleNpc(final Npc npc, Player player) throws Exception {\n              player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Hey there&#46;&#46; ;)&quot;, player));\n              player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Wanna escape this dump? Only costs 500k coins!&quot;, player));\n              player&#46;setBusy(true);\n              world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                  public void action() {\n                      owner&#46;setBusy(false);\n                String&#91;&#93; options = new String&#91;&#93;{&quot;Oh hell yeah, screw the Pmods!&quot;, &quot;Sorry, I don\'t want to break more rules&#46;&quot;};\n                owner&#46;setMenuHandler(new MenuHandler(options) {\n                    public void handleReply(final int option, final String reply) {\n                        if(owner&#46;isBusy()) {\n                            return;\n                        }\n                        owner&#46;informOfChatMessage(new ChatMessage(owner, reply, npc));\n                        owner&#46;setBusy(true);\n                        world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(owner) {\n                            public void action() {\n                                switch(option) {\n                                    case 0&#58; //Yes\n                                        world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(owner) {\n                                            public void action() {\n                                                    if(owner&#46;getInventory()&#46;countId(10) &lt; 500000) {\n                                                    owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You do not have enough money, yo!&quot;);\n                                                    running = false;\n                                                    owner&#46;setBusy(false);\n                                                    npc&#46;unblock();\n                                                }\n                                            else {\n                                                owner&#46;getInventory()&#46;remove(10, 500000);\n                                                owner&#46;getInventory()&#46;add(new InvItem(387, 1));\n                                                owner&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Spin dis shit yo and your free!&quot;, owner));\n                                                owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendInventory();\n                                                npc&#46;unblock();\n                                                owner&#46;setBusy(false);\n                                            }}\n                                        });\n                                        return;\n                                    case 1&#58; //No\n                                        owner&#46;setBusy(false);\n                                        owner&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Ok&#46; Come back when you change your mind, dawg&#46;&quot;, owner));\n                                        npc&#46;unblock();\n                                        break;\n                                    default&#58;\n                                        owner&#46;setBusy(false);\n                                        npc&#46;unblock();\n                                        return;\n                                }\n                                \n                            }\n                        });\n                    }\n                });\n                owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMenu(options);\n            }\n        });\n        npc&#46;blockedBy(player);\n    }\n    \n}[/code:1uzerlf2]He stands in the black knights jail cell where jailed players go. It costs 150k to buy a disk from him.', 'd7f5139da7b5bc42beb82928ec3b4b9c', 0, 'AIA=', '1uzerlf2', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(101, 100, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306032889, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Champions guid door', 'Requirement set to 32 quest points in order to enter...\n\nIn-game screenshot with not enough quest points:\n\n\n\nAnd the code should be added to your WallObjectAction class:\n\n[code:2e6it916]\n                        case 44&#58; // Champions Guild Door @author Yong Min\n                            if((object&#46;getX() != 150) || (object&#46;getY() != 554)) {\n                                break;\n                            }\n                            if((owner&#46;getX() == 150) &amp;&amp; (owner&#46;getY() == 553)) {\n                                if(owner&#46;getQuestPoints() &lt; 32) {\n                                    owner&#46;setBusy(true);\n                                    Npc master = world&#46;getNpc(111, 148, 152, 554, 560);\n                                    if(master != null) {\n                                        owner&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(master, &quot;Sorry! Only top adventurers are allowed in here!&quot;, owner));\n                                    }\n                                    world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(owner) {\n                                        public void action() {\n                                            owner&#46;setBusy(false);\n                                            owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You need at least 32 quest points to enter&quot;);\n                                        }\n                                    });\n                                } else {\n                                    doDoor();\n                                    owner&#46;teleport(150, 554, false);\n                                }\n                            } else {\n                                doDoor();\n                                owner&#46;teleport(150, 553, false);\n                            }\n                            break;\n[/code:2e6it916]', '2773a2cd427d5df7d72e4321127f01f7', 0, 'AIA=', '2e6it916', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(102, 101, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306032909, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Oziach', 'Briefly wrote... Will need updating when other quest options are introduced and more quest dialogue is added from other NPCs...\n\n[code:2e4nbc71]\npackage org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;npchandler;\n\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;Player;\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;Npc;\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;World;\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;InvItem;\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;ChatMessage;\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;MenuHandler;\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;event&#46;ShortEvent;\n\npublic class Oziach implements NpcHandler {\n    /**\n     * World Instance\n     */\n    public static final World world = World&#46;getWorld();\n    \n    public void handleNpc(final Npc npc, final Player player) throws Exception {\n        player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Aye&#46; Tis a fair day my friend&quot;, player));\n        player&#46;setBusy(true);\n        world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n            public void action() {\n                player&#46;setBusy(false);\n                String&#91;&#93; options = new String&#91;&#93;{&quot;Can you sell me a rune platebody?&quot;, &quot;I\'m not your friend&quot;, &quot;Yes, it\'s a very nice day&quot;};\n                player&#46;setMenuHandler(new MenuHandler(options) {\n                    public void handleReply(final int option, final String reply) {\n                        if(player&#46;isBusy()) {\n                            return;\n                        }\n                        player&#46;informOfChatMessage(new ChatMessage(player, reply, npc));\n                        player&#46;setBusy(true);\n                        world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                            public void action() {\n                                player&#46;setBusy(false);\n                                    if(option == 1) { // I\'m not your friend\n                                        player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;I\'m not your friend either!&quot;, player));\n                                        return;\n                                    }\n                                    if(option == 2) { // It\'s a nice day\n                                        player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Yes, it is isn\'t it&quot;, player));\n                                        return;\n                                    }\n                                    if(option == 0) { // Rune platebody\n                                        player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;So, how does thee know I \'ave some?&quot;, player));\n                                        world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                                            public void action() {\n                                                player&#46;informOfChatMessage(new ChatMessage(player, &quot;The guildmaster of the Champion\'s Guild told me&quot;, npc));\n                                                world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                                                    public void action() {\n                                                        player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Yes, I suppose he would, wouldn\'t he?&quot;, player));\n                                                        world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                                                            public void action() {\n                                                                player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;He\'s always sending people up to bother me!&quot;, player));\n                                                                world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                                                                    public void action() {\n                                                                        player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Well, i\'m not going to just let anyone wear my rune platemail!&quot;, player));\n                                                                        world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                                                                            public void action() {\n                                                                                player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Get out of my face and go kill the dragon to prove yourself!&quot;, player));\n                                                                                world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                                                                                    public void action() {\n                                                                                        player&#46;informOfChatMessage(new ChatMessage(player, &quot;But how can I defeat the dragon?&quot;, npc));\n                                                                                        world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                                                                                            public void action() {\n                                                                                                player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Go talk to the guildmaster&#46; He\'ll help if you are keen for a quest!&quot;, player));\n                                                                                                npc&#46;unblock();\n                                                                                            }\n                                                                                        });\n                                                                                    }\n                                                                                });\n                                                                            }\n                                                                        });\n                                                                    }\n                                                                });\n                                                            }\n                                                        });\n                                                    }\n                                                });\n                                            }\n                                        });\n                                    }\n                                }\n                            });\n                        }\n                    });\n                    player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMenu(options);\n                }\n            });\n            npc&#46;blockedBy(player);\n        }\n    }\n[/code:2e4nbc71]In your Player class, add:\n\n[code:2e4nbc71]\n    /**\n     * Dragon Slayer @author Yong Min\n     */\n    public int dragonslayer = 0;\n    \n    public void setDragonSlayerStatus(int dragonslayer) {\n        this&#46;dragonslayer = dragonslayer;\n    }\n    \n    public int getDragonSlayerStatus() {\n        return dragonslayer;\n    }\n[/code:2e4nbc71]Still in Player class, add:\n\n[code:2e4nbc71]\ndragonslayer = Integer&#46;parseInt(props&#46;getProperty(&quot;dragonslayer&quot;));\n[/code:2e4nbc71]And:\n\n[code:2e4nbc71]\npr&#46;setProperty(&quot;dragonslayer&quot;, &quot;&quot; + this&#46;getDragonSlayerStatus());\n[/code:2e4nbc71]In your Template, add:\n\n[code:2e4nbc71]\ndragonslayer=0\n[/code:2e4nbc71]', '765fdaf33cd8857881ecfc7fcfb33b5a', 0, 'AIA=', '2e4nbc71', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0);
