(146, 134, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306583681, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Kryptix game &lt;&gt; web communication', '<r><QUOTE><s>[quote]</s>Finished writing up moderator controls so they can moderate via the website. Here\'s an example of muting:<e>[/quote]</e></QUOTE>\n\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>function mutePlayer($owner, $duration) {\n        $p = new packet(0);\n        $p-&gt;addByte(12);\n        $p-&gt;addInteger($owner);\n        $p-&gt;addInteger($duration);\n        return $p-&gt;finalize();\n}<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n\n<QUOTE><s>[quote]</s>If $duration equals 0 the mute is permanant, if it\'s -1 then the player is unmuted and if it\'s anything else it\'s the timestamp they\'re muted until.<br/>\n<br/>\nFor example...<br/>\n<br/>\nmutePlayer(101, 1306777356);<br/>\n<br/>\nThat would mute me for a week.<br/>\n<br/>\nmutePlayer(101, 1308850956);<br/>\n<br/>\nMuted for a month...<br/>\n<br/>\nmutePlayer(101, 0);<br/>\n<br/>\nMute permanently...<br/>\n<br/>\nmutePlayer(101, -1);<br/>\n<br/>\nUnmute.<e>[/quote]</e></QUOTE>\n\n\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>} else if (packetID == 12) { // MUTE\n        Player p = World.getPlayerByOwner(packet.readInt());\n        if (p == null)\n                sendReply(session, 1);\n        else {\n                int duration = packet.readInt();\n               \n                if (duration == -1)\n                        p.unmute();\n                else if (duration == 0)\n                        p.mute(0);\n                else\n                        p.mute(duration);\n               \n                sendReply(session, 0);\n        }<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'afd52732e2197e331b5197530594319a', 0, 'gIA=', '2nhsshd2', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
